isValid()
Checks whether an exact LUT mapping exists.
Returns:
text
1bit

Result:
text
1

if the mapping exists.
Result:
text
0

if the mapping does not exist.

───

Syntax
Binary values:
text
.lut:isValid(
  key,
  value
)

