  LABEL1,
  LABEL2
)

Mixed usage is allowed.

───

Runnable — valid transition
Definition:
text
inline [lut] .traffic:

  labels {
    RED    = 00
    YELLOW = 01
    GREEN  = 10
  }

  data {
    RED    : GREEN
    GREEN  : YELLOW
    YELLOW : RED
  }

:

Usage:
text
1bit ok =
.traffic:isValid(
  RED,
  GREEN
)

Result:
text
1

Because:
text
RED : GREEN

exists.

───

Runnable — invalid transition
Usage:
